ictionary/镰形血球贫血症" title="lian2 xing2 xue4 qiu2 pin2 xue4 zheng4">镰形血球贫血症</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">䥥|镰[<span style="color:#cc7700;">lián</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- old variant of <a href="/dictionary/鐮">鐮</a>|<a href="/dictionary/镰">镰</a>[lian2]<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">鎌|镰[<span style="color:#cc7700;">lián</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- variant of <a href="/dictionary/鐮">鐮</a>|<a href="/dictionary/镰">镰</a>[lian2]<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">鐮|镰[<span style="color:#cc7700;">lián</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- scythe<br>- sickle<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+9570</p></div>

